   "system": {
      "description": {
         "value": "<p>When used, this box releases four bags of caltrops into the air to fall over an area within 30 feet, filling a 10-foot square area. Any creature that enters the area must succeed on a DC 15 Agility saving throw or stop moving and take 1 piercing damage. Until the creature regains at least 1 hit point, its walking speed is reduced by 10 feet. A creature moving through the area at half speed doesn't need to make the saving throw. Once used, this can be refilled with replacement caltrops. There is a 75% chance that a used bag of caltrops can be used again.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.warcraft5e.wc5e_spells.Xlhe8RDoNYnH4ob3]{Catapult}</p>",
